{"type":"message","id":"8163983c","parentId":"402146b0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:46:19.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Himalaya 没有配置文件。我需要帮助用户配置 himalaya 才能使用它来检查邮件。\n\n根据 SKILL.md，有两种配置方式：\n1. 运行交互式向导：`himalaya account configure`\n2. 手动创建配置文件\n\n由于我们在非 TTY 环境中，无法使用交互式向导。我应该告诉用户需要先配置 himalaya，并提供配置方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Himalaya 还没有配置。需要先设置 IMAP/SMTP 账户才能使用。\n\n由于当前环境不支持交互式配置，您需要手动创建配置文件。以下是配置步骤：\n\n**方法 1：在终端中运行交互式配置向导**\n```bash\nhimalaya account configure\n```\n\n**方法 2：手动创建配置文件**\n\n创建 `~/.config/himalaya/config.toml` 文件，内容如下：\n\n```toml\n[accounts.personal]\nemail = \"your-email@example.com\"\ndisplay-name = \"Your Name\"\ndefault = true\n\n# IMAP 配置（用于读取邮件）\nbackend.type = \"imap\"\nbackend.host = \"imap.example.com\"  # 例如：imap.gmail.com\nbackend.port = 993\nbackend.encryption.type = \"tls\"\nbackend.login = \"your-email@example.com\"\nbackend.auth.type = \"password\"\nbackend.auth.cmd = \"pass show email/imap\"  # 或使用 keyring\n\n# SMTP 配置（用于发送邮件）\nmessage.send.backend.type = \"smtp\"\nmessage.send.backend.host = \"smtp.example.com\"  # 例如：smtp.gmail.com\nmessage.send.backend.port = 587\nmessage.send.backend.encryption.type = \"start-tls\"\nmessage.send.backend.login = \"your-email@example.com\"\nmessage.send.backend.auth.type = \"password\"\nmessage.send.backend.auth.cmd = \"pass show email/smtp\"\n```\n\n**常见邮件服务器配置：**\n\n- **Gmail**: `imap.gmail.com:993`, `smtp.gmail.com:587`\n- **Outlook**: `outlook.office365.com:993`, `smtp.office365.com:587`\n- **QQ邮箱**: `imap.qq.com:993`, `smtp.qq.com:587`\n\n配置完成后，我就可以帮您列出最新的 5 封邮件了。您想现在配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775807159172,"responseId":"d7506fbe02cf4c78a2cba75c80998acd"}}
