{"type":"message","id":"15e68e82","parentId":"0c6d72b5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:48:50.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要重新加载 skills。在 OpenClaw 中，skills 是在启动时加载的，但用户可能想要：\n\n1. 查看当前可用的 skills\n2. 刷新/重新加载 skills 配置\n3. 或者只是想确认 skills 列表\n\n根据之前的对话，我已经列出了可用的 skills。用户说\"重新加载skills\"，这可能意味着：\n- 他们想要刷新 skills 列表\n- 或者他们安装了新的 skill 想要看到更新\n\n在 OpenClaw 中，skills 通常在会话启动时加载。我没有直接的\"重新加载 skills\"的工具。但我可以：\n1. 再次列出可用的 skills（从 available_skills 中）\n2. 告诉用户如何手动刷新（可能需要重启会话或使用 clawhub 命令）\n\n让我检查一下是否有 clawhub skill 可以用来管理 skills。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"在 OpenClaw 中，skills 在会话启动时自动加载。要重新加载 skills，您需要：\n\n**方法 1：重启会话**\n- 退出当前会话并重新启动\n\n**方法 2：使用 clawhub 管理 skills**\n\n让我检查 clawhub skill 的功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_40ff766d648f4b028ab0b7e1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/workplace/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775807318226,"responseId":"9f78f8809c9846ecaed974f60ef286ed"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b2e913ea","parentId":"15e68e82","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:48:50.920Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_40ff766d648f4b028ab0b7e1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775807330907}}
{"type":"message","id":"85838119","parentId":"b2e913ea","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:49:00.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要重新加载 skills。ClawHub CLI 可以用来管理 skills，但重新加载需要重启会话。\n\n让我检查 clawhub 是否已安装，然后列出当前安装的 skills。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查 clawhub CLI 并列出当前安装的 skills："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f32983e0b1954db78c04e154","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which clawhub && clawhub list 2>&1 || echo \"ClawHub CLI not installed\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775807330921,"responseId":"4e1d0bb3c72c4bc3bd3f86fb8f403040"}}
