{"type":"message","id":"45123c5b","parentId":"c6e06ca9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:49:16.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ClawHub CLI 已安装，但显示没有安装任何 skills。这意味着当前可用的 skills（himalaya, clawhub, coding-agent 等）是 OpenClaw 内置/预装的，而不是通过 clawhub 安装的。\n\n用户想重新加载 skills。在 OpenClaw 中：\n1. 内置 skills 在会话启动时自动加载\n2. 通过 clawhub 安装的 skills 需要重启会话才能生效\n3. 没有热重载 skills 的命令\n\n我应该解释这个情况，并提供相关选项。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"ClawHub CLI 已安装。当前显示没有通过 clawhub 安装的 skills。\n\n**当前可用的 skills 是 OpenClaw 内置/预装的：**\n- clawhub\n- coding-agent\n- gemini\n- healthcheck\n- himalaya\n- mcporter\n- node-connect\n- skill-creator\n- tmux\n- weather\n\n**重新加载 skills 的方法：**\n\n1. **重启会话** - 内置 skills 在会话启动时自动加载\n\n2. **安装新 skills** - 使用 clawhub：\n   ```bash\n   clawhub search \"关键词\"    # 搜索\n   clawhub install <skill>   # 安装\n   ```\n\n3. **更新已安装的 skills**：\n   ```bash\n   clawhub update --all      # 更新所有\n   clawhub update <skill>    # 更新指定 skill\n   ```\n\n**注意：** 新安装或更新的 skills 需要重启会话才能生效。\n\n需要我帮您搜索或安装特定的 skill 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775807342324,"responseId":"bdb8e305a8584fa19b37d810cba770c3"}}
