{"type":"message","id":"e028fd45","parentId":"40993fb0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:50:06.864Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想知道当前有哪些 skills 可用。我应该列出当前可用的 skills。根据之前的 <available_skills> 信息，我可以直接列出这些 skills。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据当前配置，**已安装并可用的 skills** 有：\n\n| Skill | 用途 |\n|-------|------|\n| **clawhub** | 搜索、安装、更新和发布 agent skills |\n| **coding-agent** | 将编码任务委托给 Codex、Claude Code 或 Pi agents |\n| **gemini** | Gemini CLI 用于问答、摘要和生成 |\n| **healthcheck** | 主机安全加固和风险容忍度配置 |\n| **himalaya** | 通过 IMAP/SMTP 管理邮件的 CLI |\n| **mcporter** | 用于直接调用 MCP servers/tools 的 CLI |\n| **node-connect** | 诊断 OpenClaw 节点连接和配对失败 |\n| **skill-creator** | 创建、编辑、改进或审核 AgentSkills |\n| **tmux** | 远程控制 tmux 会话 |\n| **weather** | 通过 wttr.in 或 Open-Meteo 获取天气和预报 |\n\n**安装更多 skills：**\n```bash\nclawhub search \"关键词\"    # 搜索\nclawhub install <skill>   # 安装\n```\n\n需要我详细介绍某个 skill 的使用方法吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775807394207,"responseId":"b564a4fa2e2e4b36b80316360d05424b"}}
