{"type":"message","id":"08ad005b","parentId":"9fcc00f7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:51:23.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了。OpenClaw 有两个 skills 目录：\n1. `/home/workplace/openclaw/skills/` - 系统/全局 skills（内置）\n2. `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` - 用户/工作区 skills\n\n用户的 imap-smtp-email skill 在工作区目录中，但没有被加载。\n\n我需要查看 OpenClaw 的配置，看看是否需要显式配置才能加载工作区 skills。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我明白了！OpenClaw 有两个 skills 目录：\n\n1. **系统 skills**: `/home/workplace/openclaw/skills/` (内置)\n2. **用户 skills**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` (您的 imap-smtp-email 在这里)\n\n**问题原因：**\n\nOpenClaw 默认只加载系统 skills。用户 skills 目录需要正确配置才能被识别。\n\n让我检查是否需要在配置中添加："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4bc8bfb364b842e296274dac","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"skills\" ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 2>&1"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fc272b8f9ff644b7b557b9e2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/_meta.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775807473327,"responseId":"523097c79aa54a8f975cb429e59fbf28"}}
